snippet.title: Monopoly City - PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
Monopoly City was published by Hasbro, Electronic Arts and Pogo Games in 2010, and was developed by Sarbakan Game Studio. And being it was a digital game, this game can no longer be officially downloaded or purchased. This is likely due to EA's license with Hasbro expiring (and being moved over to Ubisoft). Thankfully a physical CD rom copy exists... if you can find it.

Monopoly, Monopoly City (C) Hasbro
EA, EA logo, Pogo Games, pogo.com (C) Electronic Arts
